name: Stable Diffusion v1.4
creator: CompVis
description: The Stable-Diffusion-v-1-4 checkpoint was initialized with the weights of the Stable-Diffusion-v-1-2 checkpoint and subsequently fine-tuned on 225k steps at resolution 512x512 on 'laion-aesthetics v2 5+' and 10% dropping of the text-conditioning to improve classifier-free guidance sampling.

name: Stable Diffusion v1.5
creator: runwayml
description: The Stable-Diffusion-v1-5 checkpoint was initialized with the weights of the Stable-Diffusion-v1-2 checkpoint and subsequently fine-tuned on 595k steps at resolution 512x512 on 'laion-aesthetics v2 5+' and 10% dropping of the text-conditioning to improve classifier-free guidance sampling.

name: Stable Diffusion v1.5 Inpainting
creator: runwayml
description: Based off SD 1.5. Specifically made for inpainting.

name: Waifu Diffusion v1.3
creator: hakurei
description: Based off SD 1.4. Fine-tuned for anime images.

name: JWST Deep Space Diffusion
creator: dallinmackay
description: Based off SD 1.5. Makes images. Ex.) jwst, green spiral galaxy

name: Inkpunk Diffusion v2
creator: Envvi
description: Finetuned Stable Diffusion model trained on dreambooth. Vaguely inspired by Gorillaz, FLCL, and Yoji Shinkawa. 'ink splatter' can be used to increase the splotches. Its also a bit skewed to making people.

name: Dungeons and Diffusion
creator: 0xJustin
description: Makes DnD classes. See: https://huggingface.co/datasets/0xJustin/Dungeons-and-Diffusion for the available races.

name: Arcane Diffusion v3
creator: nitrosocke
description: In the style of the Arcane TV show.
